---
layout: base.njk
title: "Contact — Mudun · Get in touch"
description: "Reach Mudun for research, collaboration, or partnership on urban planning in Jordan and the region. Email hello@mudunlab.org."
---
  <section class="view active" id="view-contact">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="label" data-en="Contact" data-ar="تواصل"></span>
        <h2 data-en="Get in touch" data-ar="تواصل معنا"></h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-top:1rem"
           data-en="Questions, ideas, or collaboration — universities, NGOs, municipalities, and anyone working on cities in Jordan. The quickest way to reach us is email."
           data-ar="أسئلة أو أفكار أو تعاون — الجامعات والمنظّمات والبلديات وكلّ من يعمل على مدن الأردن. أسرع طريقة للوصول إلينا هي البريد الإلكتروني."></p>
      </div>

      <div style="max-width:640px">
        <div class="contact-lines">
          <div class="row"><span class="k" data-en="Email" data-ar="البريد"></span><a href="mailto:hello@mudunlab.org">hello@mudunlab.org</a></div>
          <div class="row"><span class="k" data-en="Based in" data-ar="المقر"></span><span data-en="Amman, Jordan" data-ar="عمّان، الأردن"></span></div>
          <div class="row"><span class="k" data-en="Collaboration" data-ar="التعاون"></span><span data-en="Email us with a short note about your organization." data-ar="راسلنا بنبذةٍ قصيرة عن جهتك."></span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="social-row">
          {% if site.social.linkedin %}<a href="{{ site.social.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4.98 3.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 1 0 5 2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5M3 9h4v12H3zM10 9h3.8v1.7h.05c.53-1 1.83-2.05 3.76-2.05C21.4 8.65 22 11 22 14.1V21h-4v-6c0-1.43-.03-3.27-2-3.27-2 0-2.3 1.56-2.3 3.17V21h-4z"/></svg>
          </a>{% endif %}
          {% if site.social.instagram %}<a href="{{ site.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
          </a>{% endif %}
          {% if site.social.facebook %}<a href="{{ site.social.facebook }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M22 12a10 10 0 1 0-11.56 9.88v-6.99H7.9V12h2.54V9.8c0-2.5 1.49-3.89 3.77-3.89 1.09 0 2.24.2 2.24.2v2.46h-1.26c-1.24 0-1.63.77-1.63 1.56V12h2.78l-.44 2.89h-2.34v6.99A10 10 0 0 0 22 12"/></svg>
          </a>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <p class="privacy" data-en="Our channels are new and still quiet — the best way to reach us is email." data-ar="قنواتنا جديدة وما زالت هادئة — وأفضل وسيلة للوصول إلينا هي البريد."></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
